reviewText: One of my favorites!!!  Love the cast.
The best ever.............these two have what it takes!!!!!!! I feel in love with these two, it will breaks my heart to find out Nadine Lustre and James Reid (JADINE LOVE TIME) breaks up!
After seeing this movie I became a fan of the JaDine love team!!!Good movie and great job!!!can't wait to see more and more movies with these two!!!
I need to order this one!
